\c 15
\s Ukuvuka kwabafileyo
\p
\v 1 Ngakho, bazalwane, ngilazisa ivangeli\x + Roma 2.16.\x* engalitshumayeza lona\x + 3.6.\x*, lani elalemukelayo\x + 11.23.\x*, njalo elimi kulo\x + 16.13. Roma 5.2. 2 Kor. 1.24. 1 Pet. 5.12.\x*,
\v 2 njalo elisindiswa ngalo\x + 1.18. Roma 1.16.\x*; uba libambelela elizwini levangeli engalitshumayela kini, ngaphandle kokuthi lakholwa ize\x + Gal. 3.4.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba ngalinika\x + 11.23.\x* okokuqala lokho engakwemukelayo\x + 11.23.\x* lami, ukuthi uKristu wafa ngenxa yezono zethu\x + Heb. 5.1,3. Joha. 1.29.\x*, njengokwemibhalo\x + Mat. 26.24. & Mark. 9.12. & Seb. 3.18.\x*;
\v 4 lokuthi wangcwatshwa; lokuthi wavuswa kwabafileyo ngosuku lwesithathu\x + Hos. 6.2. Mat. 12.40.\x*, njengokwemibhalo\x + Hlab. 2.7; 16.10. Isa. 53.10. Joha. 2.22. Seb. 2.25,31; 13.33,35; 26.22,23. 1 Pet. 1.11.\x*;
\v 5 lokuthi wabonakala\x + Luka 24.34.\x* kuKefasi\x + 1.12.\x*, emva kwalokho kwabalitshumi lambili\x + Mark. 16.14. Luka 24.36. Joha. 20.19,26. Seb. 10.41.\x*;
\v 6 emva kwalokho wabonakala ngesikhathi sinye kubazalwane abedlula amakhulu amahlanu\x + Mat. 28.17.\x*, ubunengi babo basekhona kuze kube lamuhla\x + Joha. 21.22.\x*, kodwa labanye sebalala\x + 15.18,20,51. Mat. 27.52.\x*;
\v 7 emva kwalokho wabonakala kuJakobe\x + Seb. 12.17.\x*, emva kwalokho wabonakala kubaphostoli bonke\x + Luka 24.50. Seb. 1.3,4.\x*;
\v 8 lekucineni\x + Mat. 20.6.\x* kwabo bonke wabonakala lakimi\x + 9.1. Seb. 9.3,17.\x* njengozelwe ngesikhathi esingaqondanga.
\v 9 Ngoba mina ngingomncinyanyana\x + Efe. 3.8.\x* kubaphostoli, engingafanele ukuthiwa ngumphostoli, ngoba ngazingela\x + Gal. 1.13. Seb. 8.3.\x* ibandla likaNkulunkulu.
\v 10 Kodwa ngomusa\x + Roma 1.5.\x* kaNkulunkulu ngiyikho lokho engiyikho khona, lomusa wakhe okimi kawubanga yize; kodwa ngitshikatshike\x + 2 Kor. 11.23; 12.11. Kol. 1.29.\x* okwengezelelwe kulabo bonke, kanti kungesimi\x + 3.6. 2 Kor. 3.5. Efe. 3.7. Fil. 2.13. Seb. 9.15. Mat. 10.20.\x*, kodwa ngumusa kaNkulunkulu olami.
\v 11 Ngakho loba \add kuyi\add*mi, loba \add kuyi\add*bo, ngokunjalo siyatshumayela langokunjalo lakholwa.
\p
\v 12 Kodwa uba uKristu etshunyayelwa ukuthi uvusiwe kwabafileyo, batsho njani abanye phakathi kwenu ukuthi kakukho ukuvuka kwabafileyo\x + 2 Tim. 2.18.\x*?
\v 13 Kodwa uba kungekho ukuvuka kwabafileyo, kavuswanga laye uKristu\x + 1 Thes. 4.14.\x*;
\v 14 uba-ke uKristu engavuswanga, ngakho ukutshumayela kwethu kuyize, lokholo lwenu lalo luyize.
\v 15 Lathi futhi sificwa singabafakazi bamanga bakaNkulunkulu, ngoba safakaza ngoNkulunkulu ukuthi wamvusa\x + Seb. 2.24.\x* uKristu, angamvusanga, uba-ke abafileyo bengavuswa.
\v 16 Ngoba uba abafileyo bengavuswa, kavuswanga laye uKristu;
\v 17 njalo uba uKristu engavuswanga, ukholo lwenu luyize; lisesezonweni zenu\x + Roma 4.25.\x*.
\v 18 Ngakho lalabo abalele\x + 15.6.\x* bekuKristu sebabhubha.
\v 19 Uba singabathembela kuKristu kule impilo kuphela, singabalosizi kulabo bonke abantu\x + 2 Tim. 3.12.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Kodwa khathesi-ke uKristu uvusiwe kwabafileyo\x + 1 Pet. 1.3.\x*, waba yisithelo sokuqala\x + Seb. 26.23. Joha. 14.19.\x* sabaleleyo\x + 15.6.\x*.
\v 21 Ngoba lokhu ngomuntu ukufa \add kweza\x + Joha. 11.25.\x*\add*, langomuntu ukuvuka kwabafileyo \add kweza\x + Roma 5.14,18.\x*\add*.
\v 22 Ngoba njengalokhu kuAdamu\x + Roma 5.14,18.\x* bonke bayafa, ngokunjalo futhi kuKristu bonke bazakwenziwa baphile.
\v 23 Kodwa ngulowo lalowo ngesakhe isigaba; isithelo sokuqala uKristu\x + Seb. 26.23. Joha. 14.19.\x*, besekusiba ngabakaKristu\x + 1 Thes. 4.16.\x* ekufikeni kwakhe\x + 11.26. 1 Thes. 2.19.\x*,
\v 24 besekusiba yikuphela, lapho esenikela umbuso\x + Dan. 7.14,27.\x* kuNkulunkulu, uYise\x + Efe. 5.20. Jak. 1.27.\x*, lalapho esenze kwaphela konke\x + 13.8.\x* ukubusa\x + Roma 8.38.\x* labo bonke ubukhosi lamandla\x + Roma 8.38.\x*.
\v 25 Ngoba umele yena ukubusa, aze abeke zonke izitha\x + Hlab. 110.1.\x* ngaphansi kwenyawo zakhe.
\v 26 Isitha sokucina esizachithwa yikufa\x + 13.8.\x*\x + 2 Tim. 1.10. Isam. 20.14; 21.4.\x*.
\v 27 Ngoba izinto zonke uzehlisele ngaphansi kwenyawo zakhe\x + Hlab. 8.6. Efe. 1.22. Mat. 28.18.\x*. Kodwa nxa esithi\x + Heb. 2.6.\x* izinto zonke zehlisiwe, kusobala ukuthi ungaphandle \add kwazo\add* yena ozehlisileyo izinto zonke ngaphansi kwakhe.
\v 28 Nxa izinto zonke sezehlisiwe ngaphansi kwakhe\x + Fil. 3.21.\x*, khona layo iNdodana\x + 11.3.\x* ngokwayo izazehlisa ngaphansi kwalowo owehlisela zonke izinto ngaphansi kwayo, ukuze uNkulunkulu abe yikho konke kukho konke.
\p
\v 29 Pho, bazakwenzani ababhabhathizelwa abafileyo\x + Roma 6.3.\x* uba abafileyo bengavuki isibili\x + 5.1. Mat. 5.34.\x*? Kungani babhabhathizelwa abafileyo na?
\v 30 Kungani lathi sisengozini\x + 2 Kor. 11.26. Luka 8.23.\x* ihola ngehola?
\v 31 Ngiyafa\x + 2 Kor. 4.10. Roma 8.36.\x* usuku ngosuku\x + Luka 9.23.\x*, ngiyaqinisa ngokuzincoma ngani engilakho kuKristu Jesu iNkosi yethu.
\v 32 Uba ngokwabantu ngalwa\x + 2 Kor. 1.8.\x* lezilo eEfesu\x + Seb. 18.19.\x*, nzuzo bani kimi, uba abafileyo bengavuki? Asidle sinathe\x + Tshu. 2.24. & Luka 12.19. Isa. 22.13.\x*, ngoba kusasa siyafa.
\v 33 Lingakhohliswa\x + 6.9.\x*; ukwejwayelana lababi\x + 5.6. Gal. 5.9. 2 Tim. 2.17. Seb. 17.28. Tit. 1.12.\x* kuyonakalisa izimilo ezinhle.
\v 34 Vusani ingqondo ngokulunga\x + Roma 13.11.\x* njalo lingoni; ngoba abanye balokungamazi uNkulunkulu\x + 1 Thes. 4.5.\x*; ngikhulumela ukuthi libe lenhloni\x + 6.5. 4.14.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Kodwa omunye uzakuthi: Abafileyo\x + Hez. 37.3.\x* bavuswa njani? Njalo beza lomzimba onjani?
\v 36 Siphukuphuku\x + Jak. 2.20.\x*, lokho okuhlanyelayo\x + Joha. 12.24.\x* wena, kakwenziwa kuphile ngaphandle kokuthi kufe;
\v 37 lalokho okuhlanyelayo, kawuhlanyeli umzimba ozakuba khona, kodwa uhlamvu oluze, mhlawumbe, olwebele kumbe olokunye nje\x + 14.10. 16.6.\x*;
\v 38 kodwa uNkulunkulu uyinika umzimba njengokuthanda kwakhe\x + 12.11.\x*, lakuleyo laleyo yenhlanyelo owayo umzimba.
\v 39 Inyama yonke kayisinyamanye; kodwa enye yinyama yabantu, lenye yinyama yenyamazana, lenye eyenhlanzi, lenye eyezinyoni.
\v 40 \add Ikhona\add* lemizimba yezulwini, lemizimba yemhlabeni; kodwa inkazimulo yezulu ingenye, leyemhlabeni ingenye.
\v 41 Enye yinkazimulo yelanga, lenye yinkazimulo yenyanga, lenye yinkazimulo yezinkanyezi; ngoba inkanyezi yehlukile kwenye inkanyezi enkazimulweni.
\v 42 Kunjalo-ke ukuvuka kwabafileyo\x + Dan. 12.3. Mat. 13.43.\x*. Kuhlanyelwa ekuboleni\x + 15.50. Roma 8.21. Gal. 6.8. Kol. 2.22. 2 Pet. 1.4; 2.12,19.\x*, kuyavuswa kungekho ekuboleni\x + 15.50,53,54. Roma 2.7. 2 Tim. 1.10. Efe. 6.24.\x*;
\v 43 kuhlanyelwa ekudelweni\x + Fil. 3.21. Kol. 3.4.\x*, kuvuswe enkazimulweni\x + Dan. 12.3. Mat. 13.43.\x*; kuhlanyelwa ebuthakathakeni, kuvuswe emandleni;
\v 44 kuhlanyelwa umzimba wemvelo\x + 2.14.\x*, kuvuswe umzimba womoya. Kukhona umzimba wemvelo, njalo kukhona umzimba womoya.
\v 45 Langokunjalo kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Umuntu wokuqala uAdamu waba ngumphefumulo ophilayo\x + Gen. 2.7.\x*; uAdamu wokucina ngumoya ophilisayo\x + Roma 5.14.\x*.
\v 46 Kodwa okokuqala kakusikho okomoya, kodwa okwemvelo\x + 2.14.\x*, besekusiza okomoya.
\v 47 Umuntu wokuqala\x + Joha. 3.31.\x* wavela emhlabeni, ungowomhlabathi\x + 15.48,49. Gen. 2.7 & 3.19.\x*; umuntu wesibili uyiNkosi evela ezulwini\x + Joha. 3.31.\x*\x + Joha. 3.13.\x*.
\v 48 Njengoba enjalo owomhlabathi\x + 15.48,49. Gen. 2.7; 3.19.\x*, banjalo labo abomhlabathi\x + 15.48,49. Gen. 2.7; 3.19.\x*; lanjengoba enjalo owezulwini, banjalo labo abezulwini;
\v 49 futhi njengoba sibelesimo sowomhlabathi, lathi sizakuba lesimo sowezulwini\x + Roma 8.29.\x*.
