\v 50 Kodwa ngitsho lokhu, bazalwane, ukuthi inyama legazi\x + Mat. 16.17. Joha. 3.3,5.\x* kungelidle ilifa lombuso kaNkulunkulu\x + 6.9.\x*; lokubola\x + 15.42.\x* kakulidli ilifa lokungaboli\x + 15.42.\x*.
\v 51 Khangelani, ngilitshela imfihlo: Kasiyikulala sonke\x + 1 Thes. 4.15,17.\x*\x + 15.6.\x*, kodwa sizaphendulwa sonke\x + Fil. 3.21.\x*,
\v 52 ngesikhatshana, ngokucwayiza kwelihlo, ekukhaleni kophondo lokucina; ngoba uphondo\x + Mat. 24.31. 1 Thes. 4.16. Joha. 5.25. Zek. 9.14.\x* luzakhala, labafileyo bazavuswa bengelakubola, lathi sizaphendulwa.
\v 53 Ngoba lokhu okubolayo kumele ukwembatha ukungaboli\x + 15.42.\x*, lalokho okufayo\x + 2 Kor. 5.4.\x* kwembathe ukungafi.
\v 54 Nxa-ke lokho okubolayo sekwembethe ukungaboli\x + 15.42.\x*, lalokho okufayo\x + 2 Kor. 5.4.\x* sekwembethe ukungafi, kuzakwenzeka ngalesosikhathi ilizwi elilotshiweyo \add lokuthi\add*: Ukufa\x + Isa. 25.8. Heb. 2.14,15. Isam. 20.14; 21.4.\x* kuginyiwe\x + 2 Kor. 5.4.\x* ekunqobeni\x + Mat. 12.20.\x*.
\v 55 Lungaphi, kufa\x + Hos. 13.14.\x*, udonsi lwakho? Kungaphi, ngcwaba\f + \fk ngcwaba: \fl kumbe, \fq sihogo.\f*, ukunqoba kwakho?
\v 56 Lodonsi lokufa yisono; lamandla esono ngumlayo\x + Roma 4.15.\x*.
\v 57 Kodwa kabongwe\x + Roma 7.25.\x* uNkulunkulu osinika ukunqoba\x + 1 Joha. 5.4,5. Roma 8.37.\x* ngeNkosi yethu uJesu Kristu.
\v 58 Ngakho\x + Gal. 6.9. 2 Pet. 3.14.\x*, bazalwane bami abathandekayo, manini, linganyikinyeki\x + 7.37.\x*, lengezelelwe emsebenzini weNkosi\x + 16.10. Joha. 6.28,29. Jer. 48.10.\x* kokuphela, lazi ukuthi ukutshikatshika kwenu\x + 3.8.\x* kakusilo ize eNkosini\x + 7.39.\x*.